Required Libraries/Languages:
 SystemC >= 2.2
 TLM = 2.0
 Boost Libraries >= 1.35
 Python >= 2.4
 gccxml >= 0.9 (CVS version preferred)
 Py++ >= 1.5
 pygccxml >= 1.5
 TRAP (svn version, from http://code.google.com/p/trap-gen)


In order to start the ReSP setup process, type
./waf configure --with-systemc=YOUR_SYSTEMC_FOLDER --with-tlm=YOUR_TLM_FOLDER --with-trap=YOUR_TRAP_FOLDER

For more details on ReSP and on the installation process refer to
http://code.google.com/p/resp-sim/wiki/Setup
